    public class ConsentSharingStep

      • getStepBodyClass

        public java.lang.Class getStepBodyClass()
        Description copied from class: QuestionStep
        Returns a subclass of StepBody responsible for creating the ui for answering the question, base on the AnswerFormat.

        This class is used by SurveyStepLayout to create the part of the layout where the user answers the question. For example, a StepBody for a simple text question would be responsible for creating an EditText for the SurveyStepLayout to place inside of its layout.

        Override this method with your own StepBody implementation if you create a custom QuestionStep.

        Overrides:
        getStepBodyClass in class QuestionStep
        Returns:
        the StepBody implementation for this question step.
